26
00:05:16,429 --> 00:05:18,079
<font color="yellow">I already ordered for us in advance.</font>

27
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:19,730
<font color="yellow">That's okay, right?</font>

28
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:25,329
<font color="yellow">The chef's special
