29
00:05:25,329 --> 00:05:27,329
<font color="yellow">Of course, sir.</font>

30
00:05:43,230 --> 00:05:47,129
<font color="yellow">- Hey, hey, be careful!
- Ooh, so much pressure!</font>

31
00:05:59,329 --> 00:06:02,230
<font color="yellow">Hey, make sure you take
good care of them.</font>

32
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:04,730
<font color="yellow">Yes, chef!</font>

33
00:06:14,129 --> 00:06:17,429
<font color="yellow">- Please enjoy!
- Thank you.</font>

34
00:06:20,329 --> 00:06:22,129
<font color="yellow">Let's eat.</font>

35
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:33,829
<font color="yellow">I heard the food here is great,
but I've never had a proper meal here.</font>

36
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:55,730
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

37
00:06:58,530 --> 00:07:01,329
<font color="yellow">It's okay. Give me mine
back. I'll be fine eating it.</font>

38
00:07:01,929 --> 00:07:05,530
<font color="yellow">I wanted to do that for you.
Go on and eat.</font>

39
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:15,429
<font color="yellow">How is it?
Is it good?</font>

40
00:07:56,829 --> 00:07:58,730
<font color="yellow">You're not eating?</font>

41
00:07:59,929 --> 00:08:01,929
<font color="yellow">Go ahead and eat.</font>

42
00:08:03,129 --> 00:08:04,472
<font color="yellow">But, you know...</font>

43
00:08:06,369 --> 00:08:09,730
<font color="yellow">Why did you want to see
me here, of all places?</font>

44
00:08:12,129 --> 00:08:19,929
<font color="yellow">Because I was so thankful for the
warm meals that you made for me.</font>

45
00:08:19,929 --> 00:08:24,329
<font color="yellow">So I wanted to buy you a
delicious dinner, at least once.</font>

46
00:08:24,329 --> 00:08:30,929
<font color="yellow">Even though this is nothing compared
to all you've done for me.</font>

47
00:08:33,231 --> 00:08:38,830
<font color="yellow">Also, because you
became my family.</font>

48
00:08:39,731 --> 00:08:41,929
<font color="yellow">Thank you so much.</font>

49
00:08:46,731 --> 00:08:49,929
<font color="yellow">I wanted to be sure to tell you
these things, no matter what.</font>

50
00:09:04,929 --> 00:09:11,330
<font color="yellow">I... feel great.
I kept my promise this time.</font>

51
00:09:20,731 --> 00:09:25,731
<font color="yellow">- Um...
- Today, you...</font>

52
00:09:28,330 --> 00:09:30,630
<font color="yellow">look so beautiful.</font>

53
00:09:41,530 --> 00:09:44,330
<font color="yellow">Mr. Hae Joon!
Mr. Hae Joon!</font>

54
00:09:46,231 --> 00:09:50,530
<font color="yellow">Hey, Honey!
Hey, wake up!</font>

55
00:09:50,530 --> 00:09:52,429
<font color="yellow">What do we do,
Ms. Hong Nan?</font>

56
00:09:52,429 --> 00:09:54,630
<font color="yellow">- Call the ambulance, now!
- Yes, ma'am!</font>

57
00:09:58,929 --> 00:09:59,929
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

58
00:09:59,929 --> 00:10:03,130
<font color="yellow">I... got... hit by a car.</font>

59
00:10:11,231 --> 00:10:14,929
<font color="yellow">- Will he be okay?
- Is the patient okay?</font>

60
00:10:14,929 --> 00:10:16,231
<font color="yellow">Doctor!</font>

61
00:10:20,231 --> 00:10:23,231
<font color="yellow">- What happened to him?
- It was a hit-and-run.</font>

62
00:10:23,231 --> 00:10:25,330
<font color="yellow">Let's do a thorough
examination of him first.</font>

63
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:27,130
<font color="yellow">Please stay here.</font>

64
00:10:28,731 --> 00:10:31,030
<font color="yellow">Why didn't he say something?</font>

65
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:33,530
<font color="yellow">- He'll be okay.
- Why does he do this?</font>

66
00:10:33,530 --> 00:10:36,330
<font color="yellow">Why go through such great lengths?</font>

67
00:10:42,130 --> 00:10:44,731
<font color="yellow">Round up the kids and find out
what the license plate was first.</font>

68
00:10:44,731 --> 00:10:46,929
<font color="yellow">We're in a hurry,
so make sure you do it quickly.</font>

69
00:10:46,929 --> 00:10:49,030
<font color="yellow">And call me as soon
as you find it out.</font>

70
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:51,731
<font color="yellow">Okay, got it.</font>

71
00:11:16,130 --> 00:11:18,731
<font color="yellow">Are you just going to
let him die like this?</font>

72
00:11:25,130 --> 00:11:26,630
<font color="yellow">It truly is a shame</font>

73
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:29,530
<font color="yellow">but it seems that Mr. Kim Young Soo
will be returning earlier than expected.</font>

74
00:11:29,530 --> 00:11:31,030
<font color="yellow">What kind of bullshit is that?</font>

75
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:33,130
<font color="yellow">It'll be hard for him
to live past two days.</font>

76
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:36,231
<font color="yellow">Wait, you're not saying... that
he's going to die again, right?</font>

77
00:11:36,231 --> 00:11:40,830
<font color="yellow">It can't be helped, as he
brought this upon himself.</font>

78
00:11:40,830 --> 00:11:43,429
<font color="yellow">So you want him to
die like that, again?</font>

79
00:11:43,429 --> 00:11:46,030
<font color="yellow">You're the one who made
him into Lee Hae Joon!</font>

80
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:48,330
<font color="yellow">Save him!
Now, damn it!</font>

81
00:11:52,330 --> 00:11:57,231
<font color="yellow">I cannot do anything that interferes
with the life and death of humans.</font>

82
00:11:58,830 --> 00:12:05,429
<font color="yellow">You should at least give them
time to say their goodbyes.</font>

83
00:12:06,231 --> 00:12:11,130
<font color="yellow">Bring him back to life!
What can I do?</font>

84
00:12:11,130 --> 00:12:16,231
<font color="yellow">I can't just let him die like this!</font>

85
00:12:25,429 --> 00:12:30,130
<font color="yellow">- There is one way, but...
- And what is that?</font>

86
00:12:30,130 --> 00:12:32,731
<font color="yellow">I'll do anything.</font>

87
00:12:32,731 --> 00:12:39,030
<font color="yellow">Mr. Han Gi Tak. Can you share the
time you have left with Kim Young Soo?</font>

88
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:13,429
<font color="yellow">Please, please wake up already.</font>

89
00:13:14,929 --> 00:13:18,830
<font color="yellow">If you don't,
I'll get mad at you!</font>

90
00:13:19,530 --> 00:13:23,630
<font color="yellow">You said that you'd come
and go, like the wind.</font>

91
00:13:26,429 --> 00:13:29,231
<font color="yellow">You can't do this to me.</font>

92
00:13:31,929 --> 00:13:37,429
<font color="yellow">Hurry up and wake up,
and leave our house smiling!</font>

93
00:15:25,130 --> 00:15:27,429
<font color="yellow">Let's go home.</font>

94
00:15:34,731 --> 00:15:37,130
<font color="yellow">Are... are you okay?</font>

95
00:15:39,130 --> 00:15:42,231
<font color="yellow">I want to go home.</font>

96
00:15:42,231 --> 00:15:47,929
<font color="yellow">I want to lie on my own blanket
and listen to Han Na chatter on</font>

97
00:15:47,929 --> 00:15:51,030
<font color="yellow">and eat the food
you make for me.</font>

98
00:15:59,830 --> 00:16:02,429
<font color="yellow">Yes, let's go.</font>

99
00:16:08,330 --> 00:16:10,830
<font color="yellow">Where's the patient
that was just here?</font>

100
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:13,530
<font color="yellow">- He was discharged.
- What?</font>

101
00:16:15,429 --> 00:16:18,231
<font color="yellow">- But he has a brain hemorrhage!
- What?</font>

102
00:16:33,530 --> 00:16:37,731
<font color="yellow">Geez... just what kind of trouble
did this guy cause this time?</font>

103
00:16:45,530 --> 00:16:48,731
<font color="yellow">- You're back?
- Yeah.</font>

104
00:16:48,731 --> 00:16:53,130
<font color="yellow">- Geez, makes me so worried!
- What is it now?</font>

105
00:16:53,130 --> 00:16:54,596
<font color="yellow">Cha Jae Gook!</font>

106
00:16:54,596 --> 00:16:56,501
<font color="yellow">He asked me to get dinner
with Young Chan and him</font>

107
00:16:56,501 --> 00:16:58,330
<font color="yellow">but he wouldn't smile
or even talk in front of her.</font>

108
00:16:58,330 --> 00:17:02,231
<font color="yellow">Geez, seriously.
Something's definitely off.</font>

109
00:17:02,231 --> 00:17:04,730
<font color="yellow">- Really?
- Gosh.</font>

110
00:17:06,430 --> 00:17:07,580
<font color="yellow">Oh my.</font>

111
00:17:09,505 --> 00:17:11,730
<font color="yellow">Oh my, this is me!</font>

112
00:17:13,630 --> 00:17:19,430
<font color="yellow">How long has it been?
I did this interview 10 years ago!</font>

113
00:17:19,430 --> 00:17:24,130
<font color="yellow">Wow. Your older brother sure
did collect peculiar things.</font>

114
00:17:25,930 --> 00:17:27,930
<font color="yellow">I don't know who
this lovely lady is</font>

115
00:17:27,930 --> 00:17:29,680
<font color="yellow">but she sure was pretty
10 years ago</font>

116
00:17:29,680 --> 00:17:31,430
<font color="yellow">and she still is now.</font>

117
00:17:31,430 --> 00:17:33,730
<font color="yellow">She's pretty, right?</font>

118
00:17:34,730 --> 00:17:36,730
<font color="yellow">She sure is.</font>

119
00:17:36,730 --> 00:17:43,230
<font color="yellow">Sheesh... it's been far too long.
I look so young here!</font>

120
00:17:59,529 --> 00:18:06,130
<font color="yellow">President Cha, it sure is a nice
change of pace to see you like this.</font>

121
00:18:06,130 --> 00:18:09,529
<font color="yellow">Meeting under a suspicious bridge.
How suitable, really.</font>

122
00:18:09,529 --> 00:18:11,529
<font color="yellow">I guess the thug life hasn't
been easy on you.</font>

123
00:18:12,430 --> 00:18:15,930
<font color="yellow">That's why you're going
to save me now.</font>

124
00:18:15,930 --> 00:18:17,329
<font color="yellow">We're on the same
boat, after all.</font>

125
00:18:17,329 --> 00:18:19,430
<font color="yellow">- Give me "that" first.
- Ah.</font>

126
00:18:19,430 --> 00:18:21,730
<font color="yellow">You mean, this?</font>

127
00:18:21,730 --> 00:18:24,330
<font color="yellow"><i>Kill that piece of trash!</i></font>

128
00:18:24,330 --> 00:18:26,930
<font color="yellow">Oh my, how surprising!</font>

129
00:18:26,930 --> 00:18:29,529
<font color="yellow">Now you have to show me the funds.</font>

130
00:18:35,930 --> 00:18:40,029
<font color="yellow">That'll have to be the
original recording.</font>

131
00:18:40,029 --> 00:18:42,930
<font color="yellow">Of course it's the original.</font>

132
00:18:49,329 --> 00:18:54,329
<font color="yellow">Oh my. Looks like you've
gotten yourself new buddies.</font>

133
00:18:55,130 --> 00:18:57,730
<font color="yellow">An owner can't let
his crazy dog run amok.</font>

134
00:18:57,730 --> 00:18:59,430
<font color="yellow">Crazy dog, eh?</font>

135
00:19:03,329 --> 00:19:07,029
<font color="yellow">Oh, yeah.
Did you hear?</font>

136
00:19:07,029 --> 00:19:09,930
<font color="yellow">Here I was, doing
my crazy dog thing</font>

137
00:19:09,930 --> 00:19:14,529
<font color="yellow">but he kept getting in
my way, so I ran him over.</font>

138
00:19:14,529 --> 00:19:19,529
<font color="yellow">I'm talking about your rival,
Lee Hae Joon.</font>

139
00:19:19,529 --> 00:19:23,730
<font color="yellow">What?
Lee Hae Joon?</font>

140
00:19:23,730 --> 00:19:25,730
<font color="yellow">Why would I run him over,
you may ask.</font>

141
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:28,930
<font color="yellow">Well, that's because
you ordered me to.</font>

142
00:19:28,930 --> 00:19:32,329
<font color="yellow">Just like how you told me
to kill Han Gi Tak.</font>

143
00:19:32,329 --> 00:19:35,130
<font color="yellow">So you killed him and you're
going to put the blame on me?</font>

144
00:19:35,130 --> 00:19:37,130
<font color="yellow">I've been taking your
crap this whole time</font>

145
00:19:37,130 --> 00:19:39,130
<font color="yellow">so I need some sort of insurance.</font>

146
00:19:39,130 --> 00:19:44,730
<font color="yellow">You were the one who told me to kill
Han Gi Tak and Lee Hae Joon.</font>

147
00:19:44,730 --> 00:19:47,130
<font color="yellow">You commanded me to
do all that. You did!</font>

148
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:48,930
<font color="yellow">Because we're
in the same boat.</font>

149
00:19:51,329 --> 00:19:53,829
<font color="yellow">Wow, this son of a bitch.</font>

150
00:19:53,829 --> 00:19:58,130
<font color="yellow">You dare try and blackmail me?</font>

151
00:20:04,230 --> 00:20:05,930
<font color="yellow">You're laughing?</font>

152
00:20:07,930 --> 00:20:10,529
<font color="yellow">Oh, ouch.
That hurts.</font>

153
00:20:13,730 --> 00:20:19,029
<font color="yellow">You think I brought just that
without anything to defend myself with?</font>

154
00:20:19,529 --> 00:20:24,430
<font color="yellow">Surprise!
Just you wait for it.</font>

155
00:20:33,130 --> 00:20:35,930
<font color="yellow">Find him.
Find him!</font>

156
00:20:35,930 --> 00:20:38,930
<font color="yellow">Go after him.
Hurry and find him!</font>

157
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:42,329
<font color="yellow">Damn this loach-ass bastard,
slipping away from me!</font>

158
00:20:42,329 --> 00:20:43,630
<font color="yellow">Hurry up and find him!</font>

159
00:20:48,430 --> 00:20:50,630
<font color="yellow">Find him!</font>

160
00:21:16,029 --> 00:21:18,529
<font color="yellow"><i>[Hurry up and get better, Mister]</i></font>

161
00:22:41,730 --> 00:22:44,029
<font color="yellow">Oh no, that'll leave a scar.</font>

162
00:22:52,329 --> 00:22:54,930
<font color="yellow">Good morning,
Middle-Aged Lady.</font>

163
00:22:54,930 --> 00:22:58,430
<font color="yellow">- Are you all better now?
- Yep.</font>

164
00:22:58,430 --> 00:23:01,130
<font color="yellow">I feel like I've made
a complete recovery.</font>

165
00:23:01,130 --> 00:23:04,730
<font color="yellow">That's a relief.
Come downstairs and eat.</font>

166
00:23:06,430 --> 00:23:11,029
<font color="yellow">It felt like someone kept on taking
care of me in my dreams.</font>

167
00:23:13,230 --> 00:23:17,430
<font color="yellow">Here you go.
Thank you.</font>

168
00:23:21,230 --> 00:23:24,329
<font color="yellow">Did you hear me ask for a sticker?</font>

169
00:23:44,130 --> 00:23:48,130
<font color="yellow">Oh, Ms. Maya!
I think the watch is broken!</font>

170
00:23:48,130 --> 00:23:49,630
<font color="yellow">The time I have left here
decreased by a ton!</font>

171
00:23:49,630 --> 00:23:55,430
<font color="yellow">- It's not that it's broken.
- What? What do you mean?</font>

172
00:23:55,430 --> 00:23:58,430
<font color="yellow">It's not that your time has decreased.</font>

173
00:23:58,430 --> 00:24:00,430
<font color="yellow">It's actually increased.
That's all I'll say.</font>

174
00:24:00,430 --> 00:24:02,730
<font color="yellow">Say it in a way
that I'll understand!</font>

175
00:24:02,730 --> 00:24:05,930
<font color="yellow">You'll find out when
you come back.</font>

176
00:24:05,930 --> 00:24:09,029
<font color="yellow">Just make sure you take care
of everything you need to.</font>

177
00:24:09,029 --> 00:24:11,730
<font color="yellow">This isn't nearly enough time!</font>

178
00:24:11,730 --> 00:24:14,430
<font color="yellow">It's like that for everyone.</font>

179
00:24:26,430 --> 00:24:31,230
<font color="yellow">I'm curious what your plan was for
acting oblivious this whole time.</font>

180
00:24:31,230 --> 00:24:35,730
<font color="yellow">It was to the point where I wondered if
you really were the Lee Hae Joon I know.</font>

181
00:24:35,730 --> 00:24:38,029
<font color="yellow">I couldn't trust you completely.</font>

182
00:24:38,029 --> 00:24:41,230
<font color="yellow">I believe that you said something
similar before, as well.</font>

183
00:24:41,230 --> 00:24:42,730
<font color="yellow">I'm not exactly
a trusting person.</font>

184
00:24:42,730 --> 00:24:46,230
<font color="yellow">Lee Hae Joon, the leader of
the Sunjin revitalization project.</font>

185
00:24:46,230 --> 00:24:49,529
<font color="yellow">The Chairman was
your official guardian, but</font>

186
00:24:49,529 --> 00:24:53,829
<font color="yellow">the one who protected a motherless boy
like he was his own was someone else.</font>

187
00:24:53,829 --> 00:25:00,130
<font color="yellow">And that was the Chairman's executive
secretary, which was my father.</font>

188
00:25:00,130 --> 00:25:02,730
<font color="yellow"><i>I didn't expect that at all.</i></font>

189
00:25:02,730 --> 00:25:04,630
<font color="yellow">I wanted to confirm the
results of his efforts</font>

190
00:25:04,630 --> 00:25:08,230
<font color="yellow">for the sake of Sunjin's
future, for myself.</font>

191
00:25:10,029 --> 00:25:13,829
<font color="yellow">Right now, there's a game going on that
is leaving you at a disadvantage.</font>

